Hydrogen Water Research: 100 Scientific Studies of Hydrogen Water

Hydrogen Water, Hydrogen Gas & Ionized Water
Ionized water and hydrogen water have been researched with kidneys, heart, liver, stomach, intestines, skin, brain, lungs, eyes and pretty much every part of the body has been found to benefit. The main ingredient in these waters is free-hydrogen or also known as molecular hydrogen. When it is in a free state, hydrogen is healing to the body because it attacks free-radicals and neutralizes them. The body can be helped or healed naturally with free-hydrogen antioxidants. Free-hydrogen is a unique molecule of two hydrogen, bonded together, but not bonded to any other elements. You can only get free-hydrogen in hydrogen water, hydrogen gas or ionized water. Regular water contains no free-hydrogen antioxidants.

The best way to consume free-hydrogen is in water. One of the studies, cited below, shows that the benefits of hydrogen water or ionized water (either one) will go on giving (fighting free-radicals) for days. Whereas these benefits are seen to last only hours with hydrogen gas inhaling. So, the most widely used and possibly the most therapeutic form of free-hydrogen is in hydrogen water. Hydrogen water can be produced by either a water ionizer or a hydrogen water machine, and in either case is very therapeutic, as the over 100 studies.

Regular water should not be confused with hydrogen water. It has hydrogen in it of course, H2O, but the hydrogen in regular water is not free and cannot fight free-radicals.
